Background Player
=================

This is a simple tool-set of shell scripts for controlling music playing in the background

It looks in your $XDG_MUSIC_DIR variable so make sure to set it!

Check the individual files for more help

Dependencies:
-------------
mpv
dmenu
dmenu patches:
  - https://tools.suckless.org/dmenu/patches/center/
  - https://tools.suckless.org/dmenu/patches/border/
-------------

